- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses the implementation and tradeoffs of different algorithms for SSSP. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is a possibility as the paper involves analyzing the behavior of SSSP algorithms on different types of graphs. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is a possibility as SSSP algorithms involve numerical computations. 
- cs.PF (Performance) is a possibility as the paper compares the performance of different SSSP algorithms on various input graphs.
